<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">2. Governing Equations</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1002" relname="preparation">Let be the spatial domain at time ,</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1002" relname="joint">with denoting the i -th cartesian coordinate .</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1008" relname="span">Using the Einstein summation convention , the governing equations for three-dimensional unsteady flow with variable density</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="4" relname="elaboration">( due , e. g. , to temperature variations )</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="1007" relname="same_unit">can be written as follows</segment>
